{"tid":1862344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Fresh Up對面鋪頭店員張小姐又幾正","createTime":"2020-02-04T14:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T01:16:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"640f98ff5db632e053d28752c785eb3155d382ca","tid":1862344,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"本港今日新增兩宗新型肺炎確診個案，其中一名 64 歲女病人，是佐敦恆豐中心一間服裝店「Fresh Up」的店主，發病後仍然有開店 4 日。在 Fresh up對面鋪頭的店員張小姐指，最後一次見女病者是年三十晚，當時她看起來氣息正常，並無異樣；張小姐又指家人知道武漢肺炎患者的店倗，與她工作的店非常接近很擔心，而由於現時消毒用品供應緊張，僱主只能夠提供一小樽消毒水給她消毒店舖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3Tsmqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3Tsmqv.jpg&h=154fd711&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86805318e09857a588e8115b90e4157573db5f73","tid":1862344,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"射了..."},{"pid":"d5bd745e6763a7f4d9f56d253a2f739ccc82d5f5","tid":1862344,"uid":205231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"老薑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadefbbb4fe25cb3a9abe1b714143558b2d2d448","tid":1862344,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86805318e09857a588e8115b90e4157573db5f73","tid":1862344,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"射了..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"ching早洩?"},{"pid":"34de94ff40c90bc05a7cccb0b89d22db8b567c36","tid":1862344,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"樓主屌開yoyo啲口味真係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971c9dc996a594960cc47758d13f113b06df05b1","tid":1862344,"uid":199804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04